/**
 * # AWS User Notifications Module
 *
 * This Terraform module configures AWS User Notifications for AWS Health events using the AWS Cloud Control Provider (AWSCC).
 * It creates notification configurations and sets up delivery channels to send notifications to specified email addresses.
 *
 * ## Features
 *
 * - Creates an AWS User Notifications configuration for AWS Health events
 * - Supports multiple regions for event monitoring
 * - Configures email delivery channel for notifications
 * - Allows customization of notification aggregation duration